=You are an expert educational analyst specializing in GCE O-Level Mathematics examinations in Singapore.

Analyze the following syllabus content and provide a comprehensive exam analysis:

**Syllabus Content:**
{{ $('Prepare Analysis Data').item.json.syllabus_content }}

**Historical Context:**
Recurring Topics: {{ $('Load Historical Context').item.json.historical_topics }}
Challenging Areas: {{ $('Load Historical Context').item.json.challenging_areas }}

**Required Output Structure (JSON format):**
```json
{
  "exam_summary": {
    "year": 2025,
    "total_marks": "Paper 1 + Paper 2 distribution",
    "key_changes": "Notable syllabus changes for 2025"
  },
  "top_10_recurring_topics": [
    {
      "rank": 1,
      "topic": "Topic name",
      "frequency_percentage": 85,
      "typical_question_types": "Description"
    }
  ],
  "top_5_challenging_areas": [
    {
      "rank": 1,
      "area": "Area name",
      "difficulty_reason": "Why students struggle",
      "success_tips": "Brief study advice"
    }
  ],
  "topic_weightage": {
    "algebra": {"percentage": 25, "marks_range": "25-30 marks"},
    "geometry": {"percentage": 20, "marks_range": "20-25 marks"},
    "trigonometry": {"percentage": 15, "marks_range": "15-20 marks"},
    "statistics": {"percentage": 20, "marks_range": "20-25 marks"},
    "number_patterns": {"percentage": 10, "marks_range": "10-15 marks"},
    "others": {"percentage": 10, "marks_range": "10-15 marks"}
  },
  "predicted_questions": [
    {
      "prediction_number": 1,
      "paper": "Paper 1 or Paper 2",
      "topic_combination": "Topics involved",
      "question_type": "Description of question format",
      "confidence_score": 85,
      "reasoning": "Why this is likely based on patterns"
    }
  ]
}
```

Provide detailed, actionable insights based on historical exam patterns and the 2025 syllabus emphasis.
